{"repo": "freqtrade/freqtrade-strategies", "pull_number": 325, "instance_id": "freqtrade__freqtrade-strategies-325", "issue_numbers": [324], "base_commit": "b8a90bebebfc13a78416635166ebafdece596d3f", "patch": "diff --git a/user_data/strategies/futures/FAdxSmaStrategy.py b/user_data/strategies/futures/FAdxSmaStrategy.py\nindex 28729d57e..3bb13caf0 100644\n--- a/user_data/strategies/futures/FAdxSmaStrategy.py\n+++ b/user_data/strategies/futures/FAdxSmaStrategy.py\n@@ -53,9 +53,9 @@ class FAdxSmaStrategy(IStrategy):\n     pos_exit_adx = DecimalParameter(15, 40, decimals=1, default=30.0, space=\"sell\")\n \n     # Define the parameter spaces\n-    adx_period = IntParameter(4, 24, default=14)\n-    sma_short_period = IntParameter(4, 24, default=12)\n-    sma_long_period = IntParameter(12, 175, default=48)\n+    adx_period = IntParameter(4, 24, default=14, space='buy')\n+    sma_short_period = IntParameter(4, 24, default=12, space='buy')\n+    sma_long_period = IntParameter(12, 175, default=48, space='buy')\n \n     def populate_indicators(self, dataframe: DataFrame, metadata: dict) -> DataFrame:\n \n", "test_patch": "", "problem_statement": "FAdxSmaStrategy fails to load due to adx_period parameter space error\n## Describe your environment\n\n  * Operating system: Windows 11\n  * Python Version: Python 3.13.8\n  * CCXT version: 4.5.27\n  * Freqtrade Version: freqtrade docker-2025.12-dev-eb3e8b82\n  * Strategy: FAdxSmaStrategy.py\n\n## Describe the problem:\n\nWhen running the futures strategy FAdxSmaStrategy using FreqUI, Freqtrade fails during strategy initialization and throws an exception stating that it cannot determine the parameter space for adx_period.\n\nThis happens even when running the strategy with default parameters and without explicitly enabling hyperopt.\n\n### Steps to reproduce:\n\n  1. Start FreqUI\n  2. Select strategy FAdxSmaStrategy\n  3. Run the strategy beaktesting using default parameters\n  4. The backtest fails immediately during strategy initialization\n\n### Observed Results:\n\n  * What happened?\n    Backtesting fails with the following error:\n\n    ```\n    freqtrade.exceptions.OperationalException:\n    Cannot determine parameter space for adx_period.\n    ```\n  * What did you expect to happen?\n    The strategy should load successfully and start backtesting with default parameters, or provide a clearer error message indicating which parameter definition is invalid.\n\n### Relevant code exceptions or logs\n\nNote: Please copy/paste text of the messages, no screenshots of logs please.\n\n  ```\n2025-12-20 13:51:40,371 - freqtrade.rpc.api_server.api_backtest - ERROR - Backtesting caused an error: Cannot determine\nparameter space for adx_period.\nTraceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"/freqtrade/freqtrade/rpc/api_server/api_backtest.py\", line 93, in __run_backtest_bg\n    min_date, max_date = ApiBG.bt[\"bt\"].backtest_one_strategy(\n                         ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~^\n        strat, ApiBG.bt[\"data\"], ApiBG.bt[\"timerange\"]\n        ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\n    )\n    ^\n  File \"/freqtrade/freqtrade/optimize/backtesting.py\", line 1751, in backtest_one_strategy\n    self._set_strategy(strat)\n    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~^^^^^^^\n  File \"/freqtrade/freqtrade/optimize/backtesting.py\", line 299, in _set_strategy\n    self.strategy.ft_bot_start()\n    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~^^\n  File \"/freqtrade/freqtrade/strategy/interface.py\", line 219, in ft_bot_start\n    self.ft_load_hyper_params(self.config.get(\"runmode\") == RunMode.HYPEROPT)\n    ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^\n  File \"/freqtrade/freqtrade/strategy/hyper.py\", line 93, in ft_load_hyper_params\n    self._ft_hyper_params = detect_all_parameters(self)\n                            ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~^^^^^^\n  File \"/freqtrade/freqtrade/strategy/hyper.py\", line 182, in detect_all_parameters\n    raise OperationalException(f\"Cannot determine parameter space for {attr_name}.\")\nfreqtrade.exceptions.OperationalException: Cannot determine parameter space for adx_period.\n  ```\n\n", "hints_text": "\n\n", "all_hints_text": "\n\n", "commit_urls": ["https://github.com/freqtrade/freqtrade-strategies/commit/d2e8721595931d9c5f4504acfeea381bc3f416e4"], "created_at": "2025-12-20T14:40:38Z"}
